{"tid":2110809,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.21元朗襲擊事件再多1名市民申請加入訴訟","createTime":"2020-07-16T07:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T07:24:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe80322c61aa9aacff7789f7f4823919b8454d0a","tid":2110809,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"民主黨立法會議員林卓廷早前與數名在去年7月21日在元朗一帶受傷的市民入稟控告警務處處長鄧炳強，林卓廷說，再多一名當晚在雞地受襲的市民蘇先生申請加入訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷說，訴訟已時進入關鍵階段，蘇先生是一名十分重要的證人，加入對訴訟十分重要，高等法院會在7月21日舉行聆訊，決定蘇先生是否能夠加入訴訟，如果成功，就共有9位傷者共同入稟。<br />\n<br />\n本台《鏗鏘集》日前報道，去年7.21有懷疑便裝警員多次在鳳攸北街徘徊，但沒有對手持棍棒、竹枝的集結白衣人採取行動。警方回覆查詢時，沒有確認片段中的人是否便衣警員。警方昨晚表示，7.21當日元朗警區曾經派出便裝警員，到人羣集結地方視察，並因應現場情況及風險評估，作出部署及行動。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷批評，警方由頭到尾都目擊過程，但卻作出零部署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538097-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538097-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3yvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=2ef1f2b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538097-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ee57d97c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538097-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"96863145b84709dedd82de6f2a74f5dc8798336b","tid":2110809,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f73efca721732600ec561caa4c9f7cfb569647e","tid":2110809,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"7.21 唔見人"},{"pid":"9648f42d3b027bf6ebfd73db5c9efe4aa2e327e6","tid":2110809,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f73efca721732600ec561caa4c9f7cfb569647e","tid":2110809,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07